<p>blivet-gui is a graphical application to manage disks, partitions and LVM2 storages.
As backend it uses <link href="https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Blivet">blivet</link>, powerful python module for storage configuration.</p>

<p>This guide will help you with some basic tasks regarding partitioning and creating and managing LVM2 storages.</p>

